    <updated>2025-01-11T11:12:21.938000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>gregorw</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/12545</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi Marty,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;ony usecase that I just came around is the maybe missing support for Variant Configuration in the OData API. Only the new &lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_S4HANA_CLOUD/03c04db2a7434731b7fe21dca77440da/6ebc3bdc52d84df395f852b22f927dd8.html?locale=en-US" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;OData v4 Sales Order API&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;supports Variant Configuration. If you need Variant Configuration also for Inquiries or Sales Quotations then the only option is the&amp;nbsp;&lt;SPAN&gt;BAPI_INQUIRY_CREATEFROMDATA2 or&amp;nbsp;BAPI_QUOTATION_CREATEFROMDATA2.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Best Regards&lt;BR /&gt;Gregor&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/re-s-4-public-cloud-rfc-call/qaq-p/13983150/comment-id/4898704#M4898704"/>
    <published>2025-01-11T11:12:21.938000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
